  "text": "Several new bladder cancer diagnostic tests have been recently approved and many more are undergoing development and investigation [CITATION_1] . However, because the Food and Drug Administration (FDA) approval process does not require any proof of cost-effectiveness, new tests almost always mean higher costs of care [CITATION_2] .",
